import { Color } from './color'
import { Font } from './font'
import { TextStyle, TextStyles } from './textStyle'
import { Layout } from './layout'

const Luna = {
  color: { ...Color },
  font: { ...Font },
  TextStyle: { ...TextStyle },
  TextStyles: { ...TextStyles },
  layout: { ...Layout },
}

export { Luna }
